summary: Several presets from none other than the not so famous Lord Burnch
descriptionHtml:
[size=2]The fine craftsmanship and talent of Lord Burnch characters is now available to all who use [/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?][size=2]Racemenu[/size][/url][size=2]! I intend to update this mod regularly with additional presets.

The requirements to achieve the 'exact' likeness of each preset is listed with it's picture.
